            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Through the <code>POST</code> request's URL, let the server know that the data you're sending is a new article.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"bash\" name=\"Console Editor\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"POST https://fakenews.com/article\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;title&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\": \" /><text value=\"&quot;UFOs sighted&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\",\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;content&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\": \" /><text value=\"&quot;Believe it or not ...&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"26\" /><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"33\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>/</code>, followed by <code>article</code>.</p></body></html>"
